high_descs: walk forward to the end of the room, then turn left and walk over to the kitchen table there
grab a loaf of bread off of the kitchen table
turn left and walk over to the fridge in the right side corner of the room
place the bread inside the fridge to cool, then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the table at the end of the room
place the bread down on the table there
anns.task_desc: place a cooled loaf of bread down on the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn left, step forward, then turn left to face the end of the white table.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the end of the white table.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the fridge.
Cool the bread in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and then turn right to face the end of the white table.
Place the loaf of bread on the white table.
anns.task_desc: To cool a loaf of bread as well as return it to the white table.

high_descs: Go forward to the counter, then turn left to go to the wall, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the bread on the table.
Turn left and go forward, then turn right and go to the wall, then turn left to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the bread inside, wait, then take it out.
Turn around and go toward the wall in front of you, then turn right to face the table.
Place the bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put cold bread on the table.
